---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Home
---
<h2>zerm Port</h2>
<p>This repository is an Eleventy 3.1.5 + Luxon port of the Zola <strong>zerm</strong> theme.</p>
<p>Original theme: <a href="https://github.com/ejmg/zerm">https://github.com/ejmg/zerm</a></p>
<p>Live demo: <a href="https://zerm.ejmg.now.sh/">https://zerm.ejmg.now.sh/</a></p>
<h3>Recent Posts</h3>
{% for post in collections.posts %}
  <article class="post-card h-entry">
    <h4 class="p-name"><a class="u-url" href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h4>
    <p><time class="dt-published" datetime="{{ post.date | htmlDateString }}">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</time></p>
    <p class="p-summary">{{ post.data.description or "" }}</p>
  </article>
{% endfor %}
